    A sociologist of the economy, who after a long time at MIT has returned to France, Vincent brings the AIME project in his role as mediator, a fine-grained understanding of the social sciences and the world of finance. Having participated in research projects that pushed the analysis of the science of economics as a science — research that is of major importance to the project — he has allowed us to push the inquiry further and deeper than before, as well as mobilize co-inquirers from Europe and the United States.
  </p>
