    Teaching in London, Noortje comes from the Dutch school of “science studies” and has played a decisive role in developing the inquiry on those questions related to politics. Ever since she began researching, Noortje has combined extremely close attention to political philosophy and the power of “digital methods”. Having her as a mediator on political issues has allowed the inquiry to take advantage of the innovative techniques that she has developed to investigate controversies in technology as well as those in empirical philosophy.
